Revision history for Perinci-Sub-To-Text

0.29     2013-11-16 (SHARYANTO)

         - Observe arg spec's 'default' property (Rinci 1.1.42).


0.28     2013-11-01 (SHARYANTO)

         [INCOMPATIBLE CHANGES]

         - Instead of accepting 'url' (use Riap), now accept 'name' and 'meta'.
           This decouples the module from using Riap and make the module more
           reusable. This change is motivated by writing App-riap.


0.27     2013-10-02 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional change. Forgot to add 'use utf8'.


0.26     2013-10-02 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional change. Add French translation.


0.25     2013-09-08 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional change. Replace Perinci::Access::InProcess with ::Perl.


0.24     2013-08-11 (SHARYANTO)

         - Prefix internal attributes with '_doc' to avoid clashes (e.g. with
           Perinci::CmdLine's _res).


0.23     2013-08-11 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Update log statement.


0.22     2013-08-05 (SHARYANTO)

         - Fix a small bug.


0.21     2013-07-26 (SHARYANTO)

         - Fix a small bug.


0.20     2013-07-26 (SHARYANTO)

         - First release. Extracted from Perinci-To-Text to allow generating
           documentation for a specific function only (and not the whole
           package). Version number starts from 0.20 because some modules are
           moved here.
